{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u68645c3c\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Loader 的链式调用顺序不仅会影响结果，而且极其关键。</span></strong></p><p id=\"ufbdec831\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">在 Webpack 中，Loader 的执行遵循 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从右到左”</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 或 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从下到上”</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 的逆序执行逻辑（类似函数组合 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose(f, g, h)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">）。</span></p><p id=\"uaeb8f2c7\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">为什么顺序很重要？</span></strong></p><p id=\"uebfeb796\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">因为每一个 Loader 实际上是将上一个 Loader 处理后的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输出</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">作为自己的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输入</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">。如果顺序颠倒，输入的数据格式就会报错。</span></p><p id=\"u408587b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">以处理 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Sass/SCSS</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 文件为例，标准配置顺序如下：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"ypLYV\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>module: {\n  rules: [\n    {\n      test: /\\.scss$/,\n      use: [\n        'style-loader', // 3. 将 JS 中的样式字符串插入到 HTML 的 &lt;style&gt; 标签中\n        'css-loader',   // 2. 将 CSS 转换成 CommonJS 模块（处理 url() 和 @import）\n        'sass-loader'   // 1. 将 Sass 代码编译成 CSS\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</code></pre><p id=\"u4fdf2974\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">如果顺序反了会怎样？</span></strong></p><p id=\"u07532917\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">假设你将顺序改为</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">['sass-loader', 'css-loader', 'style-loader']</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：</span></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u9377d161\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">style-loader</span></strong></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">首先尝试运行，但它接收到的是原始的</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">.scss</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">源码，它根本看不懂，直接崩溃。</span></li><li id=\"u1474496e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">即使强制运行，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">sass-loader</span></strong></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 最终产出的是标准的 CSS 文本，但此时已经没有任何 Loader 负责将其注入到 DOM 中，导致样式失效。</span></li></ol><p id=\"uc0faa282\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">核心原理：Compose（组合）</span></strong></p><p id=\"u1a4dfd82\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Webpack 内部使用类似函数式编程的</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">逻辑。当你写</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">[A, B, C]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">时，执行顺序是：<br /></span><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">result = A(B(C(source)))</span></strong></code></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc082d3b0\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Pitch 阶段</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从左往右（A -&gt; B -&gt; C），用于拦截或处理元数据。</span></li><li id=\"uc64a44c8\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Normal 阶段</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从右往左（C -&gt; B -&gt; A），用于转换代码内容。</span></li></ul></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u68645c3c\" id=\"u68645c3c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc879edbc\" id=\"uc879edbc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Loader 的链式调用顺序不仅会影响结果，而且极其关键。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufbdec831\" id=\"ufbdec831\"><span data-lake-id=\"uebcb04b8\" id=\"uebcb04b8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">在 Webpack 中，Loader 的执行遵循 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u81c48446\" id=\"u81c48446\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从右到左”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubb7a7197\" id=\"ubb7a7197\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 或 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc537ea4c\" id=\"uc537ea4c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从下到上”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc2ca6e7f\" id=\"uc2ca6e7f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 的逆序执行逻辑（类似函数组合 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud9312252\" id=\"ud9312252\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0597f046\" id=\"u0597f046\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose(f, g, h)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u207995ad\" id=\"u207995ad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaeb8f2c7\" id=\"uaeb8f2c7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2c40381c\" id=\"u2c40381c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">为什么顺序很重要？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uebfeb796\" id=\"uebfeb796\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02d31c07\" id=\"u02d31c07\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">因为每一个 Loader 实际上是将上一个 Loader 处理后的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udf909a8a\" id=\"udf909a8a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输出</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5283eeac\" id=\"u5283eeac\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">作为自己的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uff0ba3ce\" id=\"uff0ba3ce\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输入</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue18e0086\" id=\"ue18e0086\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">。如果顺序颠倒，输入的数据格式就会报错。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u408587b9\" id=\"u408587b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u860f7454\" id=\"u860f7454\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">以处理 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua5514785\" id=\"ua5514785\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Sass/SCSS</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u55d163a6\" id=\"u55d163a6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 文件为例，标准配置顺序如下：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22module%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20rules%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20test%3A%20%2F%5C%5C.scss%24%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20use%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'style-loader'%2C%20%2F%2F%203.%20%E5%B0%86%20JS%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%20HTML%20%E7%9A%84%20%3Cstyle%3E%20%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E4%B8%AD%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'css-loader'%2C%20%20%20%2F%2F%202.%20%E5%B0%86%20CSS%20%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E6%88%90%20CommonJS%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%20url()%20%E5%92%8C%20%40import%EF%BC%89%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'sass-loader'%20%20%20%2F%2F%201.%20%E5%B0%86%20Sass%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E6%88%90%20CSS%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%5D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22Github%20Light%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ypLYV%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u4fdf2974\" id=\"u4fdf2974\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u21cd49f3\" id=\"u21cd49f3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">如果顺序反了会怎样？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u07532917\" id=\"u07532917\"><span data-lake-id=\"u064c5377\" id=\"u064c5377\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">假设你将顺序改为</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc5959520\" id=\"uc5959520\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1b26ced0\" id=\"u1b26ced0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27affb8d\" id=\"u27affb8d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">['sass-loader', 'css-loader', 'style-loader']</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u57863fd8\" id=\"u57863fd8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：</span></p><ol list=\"uc0423783\"><li fid=\"u16710981\" data-lake-id=\"u9377d161\" id=\"u9377d161\"><code data-lake-id=\"uafe0d97f\" id=\"uafe0d97f\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4a0705cd\" id=\"u4a0705cd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">style-loader</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7783915f\" id=\"u7783915f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"uff028f56\" id=\"uff028f56\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">首先尝试运行，但它接收到的是原始的</span><span data-lake-id=\"u7e71f681\" id=\"u7e71f681\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1f1596a6\" id=\"u1f1596a6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud4a1315c\" id=\"ud4a1315c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">.scss</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf2a0d80a\" id=\"uf2a0d80a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u78dfc2f0\" id=\"u78dfc2f0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">源码，它根本看不懂，直接崩溃。</span></li><li fid=\"u16710981\" data-lake-id=\"u1474496e\" id=\"u1474496e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u99c0b7bd\" id=\"u99c0b7bd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">即使强制运行，</span><code data-lake-id=\"ucf77b1c1\" id=\"ucf77b1c1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6b37955e\" id=\"u6b37955e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">sass-loader</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4713646d\" id=\"u4713646d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 最终产出的是标准的 CSS 文本，但此时已经没有任何 Loader 负责将其注入到 DOM 中，导致样式失效。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"uc0faa282\" id=\"uc0faa282\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0522c924\" id=\"u0522c924\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">核心原理：Compose（组合）</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a4dfd82\" id=\"u1a4dfd82\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud474d320\" id=\"ud474d320\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Webpack 内部使用类似函数式编程的</span><span data-lake-id=\"u4a8d9b6a\" id=\"u4a8d9b6a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u62ab34d9\" id=\"u62ab34d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u01bf958a\" id=\"u01bf958a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucb231255\" id=\"ucb231255\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u677a746d\" id=\"u677a746d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">逻辑。当你写</span><span data-lake-id=\"u20fe0949\" id=\"u20fe0949\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3f26af56\" id=\"u3f26af56\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9ffbc704\" id=\"u9ffbc704\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">[A, B, C]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u51ed384f\" id=\"u51ed384f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"ud58a039e\" id=\"ud58a039e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">时，执行顺序是：<br /></span><code data-lake-id=\"u02454358\" id=\"u02454358\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u229a4965\" id=\"u229a4965\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">result = A(B(C(source)))</span></strong></code></p><ul list=\"ue73b5618\"><li fid=\"u51a654b1\" data-lake-id=\"uc082d3b0\" id=\"uc082d3b0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf2107122\" id=\"uf2107122\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Pitch 阶段</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2a926be\" id=\"ub2a926be\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从左往右（A -&gt; B -&gt; C），用于拦截或处理元数据。</span></li><li fid=\"u51a654b1\" data-lake-id=\"uc64a44c8\" id=\"uc64a44c8\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ueb7409d9\" id=\"ueb7409d9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Normal 阶段</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6841c8f3\" id=\"u6841c8f3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从右往左（C -&gt; B -&gt; A），用于转换代码内容。</span></li></ul>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u68645c3c\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Loader 的链式调用顺序不仅会影响结果，而且极其关键。</span></strong></p><p id=\"ufbdec831\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">在 Webpack 中，Loader 的执行遵循 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从右到左”</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 或 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从下到上”</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 的逆序执行逻辑（类似函数组合 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose(f, g, h)</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">）。</span></p><p id=\"uaeb8f2c7\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">为什么顺序很重要？</span></strong></p><p id=\"uebfeb796\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">因为每一个 Loader 实际上是将上一个 Loader 处理后的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输出</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">作为自己的</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输入</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">。如果顺序颠倒，输入的数据格式就会报错。</span></p><p id=\"u408587b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">以处理 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Sass/SCSS</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 文件为例，标准配置顺序如下：</span></p><pre data-language=\"javascript\" id=\"ypLYV\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-javascript\"><code>module: {\n  rules: [\n    {\n      test: /\\.scss$/,\n      use: [\n        'style-loader', // 3. 将 JS 中的样式字符串插入到 HTML 的 &lt;style&gt; 标签中\n        'css-loader',   // 2. 将 CSS 转换成 CommonJS 模块（处理 url() 和 @import）\n        'sass-loader'   // 1. 将 Sass 代码编译成 CSS\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</code></pre><p id=\"u4fdf2974\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">如果顺序反了会怎样？</span></strong></p><p id=\"u07532917\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">假设你将顺序改为</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">['sass-loader', 'css-loader', 'style-loader']</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：</span></p><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u9377d161\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">style-loader</span></strong></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">首先尝试运行，但它接收到的是原始的</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">.scss</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">源码，它根本看不懂，直接崩溃。</span></li><li id=\"u1474496e\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">即使强制运行，</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">sass-loader</span></strong></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 最终产出的是标准的 CSS 文本，但此时已经没有任何 Loader 负责将其注入到 DOM 中，导致样式失效。</span></li></ol><p id=\"uc0faa282\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">核心原理：Compose（组合）</span></strong></p><p id=\"u1a4dfd82\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Webpack 内部使用类似函数式编程的</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">逻辑。当你写</span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">[A, B, C]</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">时，执行顺序是：<br /></span><code class=\"ne-code\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">result = A(B(C(source)))</span></strong></code></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc082d3b0\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Pitch 阶段</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从左往右（A -&gt; B -&gt; C），用于拦截或处理元数据。</span></li><li id=\"uc64a44c8\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Normal 阶段</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从右往左（C -&gt; B -&gt; A），用于转换代码内容。</span></li></ul></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u68645c3c\" id=\"u68645c3c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc879edbc\" id=\"uc879edbc\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Loader 的链式调用顺序不仅会影响结果，而且极其关键。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufbdec831\" id=\"ufbdec831\"><span data-lake-id=\"uebcb04b8\" id=\"uebcb04b8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">在 Webpack 中，Loader 的执行遵循 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u81c48446\" id=\"u81c48446\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从右到左”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubb7a7197\" id=\"ubb7a7197\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 或 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc537ea4c\" id=\"uc537ea4c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">“从下到上”</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc2ca6e7f\" id=\"uc2ca6e7f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 的逆序执行逻辑（类似函数组合 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud9312252\" id=\"ud9312252\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0597f046\" id=\"u0597f046\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose(f, g, h)</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u207995ad\" id=\"u207995ad\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">）。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaeb8f2c7\" id=\"uaeb8f2c7\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2c40381c\" id=\"u2c40381c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">为什么顺序很重要？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"uebfeb796\" id=\"uebfeb796\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02d31c07\" id=\"u02d31c07\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">因为每一个 Loader 实际上是将上一个 Loader 处理后的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udf909a8a\" id=\"udf909a8a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输出</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5283eeac\" id=\"u5283eeac\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">作为自己的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uff0ba3ce\" id=\"uff0ba3ce\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">输入</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue18e0086\" id=\"ue18e0086\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">。如果顺序颠倒，输入的数据格式就会报错。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u408587b9\" id=\"u408587b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u860f7454\" id=\"u860f7454\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">以处理 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua5514785\" id=\"ua5514785\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Sass/SCSS</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u55d163a6\" id=\"u55d163a6\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 文件为例，标准配置顺序如下：</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22javascript%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22module%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20rules%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20test%3A%20%2F%5C%5C.scss%24%2F%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20use%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'style-loader'%2C%20%2F%2F%203.%20%E5%B0%86%20JS%20%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%20HTML%20%E7%9A%84%20%3Cstyle%3E%20%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E4%B8%AD%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'css-loader'%2C%20%20%20%2F%2F%202.%20%E5%B0%86%20CSS%20%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E6%88%90%20CommonJS%20%E6%A8%A1%E5%9D%97%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%20url()%20%E5%92%8C%20%40import%EF%BC%89%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20'sass-loader'%20%20%20%2F%2F%201.%20%E5%B0%86%20Sass%20%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E6%88%90%20CSS%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%5D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%5D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22Github%20Light%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ypLYV%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u4fdf2974\" id=\"u4fdf2974\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u21cd49f3\" id=\"u21cd49f3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">如果顺序反了会怎样？</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u07532917\" id=\"u07532917\"><span data-lake-id=\"u064c5377\" id=\"u064c5377\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">假设你将顺序改为</span><span data-lake-id=\"uc5959520\" id=\"uc5959520\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1b26ced0\" id=\"u1b26ced0\"><span data-lake-id=\"u27affb8d\" id=\"u27affb8d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">['sass-loader', 'css-loader', 'style-loader']</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u57863fd8\" id=\"u57863fd8\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：</span></p><ol list=\"uc0423783\"><li fid=\"u16710981\" data-lake-id=\"u9377d161\" id=\"u9377d161\"><code data-lake-id=\"uafe0d97f\" id=\"uafe0d97f\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4a0705cd\" id=\"u4a0705cd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">style-loader</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id=\"u7783915f\" id=\"u7783915f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"uff028f56\" id=\"uff028f56\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">首先尝试运行，但它接收到的是原始的</span><span data-lake-id=\"u7e71f681\" id=\"u7e71f681\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u1f1596a6\" id=\"u1f1596a6\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud4a1315c\" id=\"ud4a1315c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">.scss</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf2a0d80a\" id=\"uf2a0d80a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u78dfc2f0\" id=\"u78dfc2f0\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">源码，它根本看不懂，直接崩溃。</span></li><li fid=\"u16710981\" data-lake-id=\"u1474496e\" id=\"u1474496e\"><span data-lake-id=\"u99c0b7bd\" id=\"u99c0b7bd\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">即使强制运行，</span><code data-lake-id=\"ucf77b1c1\" id=\"ucf77b1c1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6b37955e\" id=\"u6b37955e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">sass-loader</span></strong></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4713646d\" id=\"u4713646d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> 最终产出的是标准的 CSS 文本，但此时已经没有任何 Loader 负责将其注入到 DOM 中，导致样式失效。</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"uc0faa282\" id=\"uc0faa282\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0522c924\" id=\"u0522c924\" class=\"lake-fontsize-14\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">核心原理：Compose（组合）</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a4dfd82\" id=\"u1a4dfd82\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud474d320\" id=\"ud474d320\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Webpack 内部使用类似函数式编程的</span><span data-lake-id=\"u4a8d9b6a\" id=\"u4a8d9b6a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u62ab34d9\" id=\"u62ab34d9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u01bf958a\" id=\"u01bf958a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">compose</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucb231255\" id=\"ucb231255\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"u677a746d\" id=\"u677a746d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">逻辑。当你写</span><span data-lake-id=\"u20fe0949\" id=\"u20fe0949\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3f26af56\" id=\"u3f26af56\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9ffbc704\" id=\"u9ffbc704\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">[A, B, C]</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u51ed384f\" id=\"u51ed384f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\"> </span><span data-lake-id=\"ud58a039e\" id=\"ud58a039e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">时，执行顺序是：<br /></span><code data-lake-id=\"u02454358\" id=\"u02454358\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u229a4965\" id=\"u229a4965\" class=\"lake-fontsize-11\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10); background-color: rgb(240, 242, 245)\">result = A(B(C(source)))</span></strong></code></p><ul list=\"ue73b5618\"><li fid=\"u51a654b1\" data-lake-id=\"uc082d3b0\" id=\"uc082d3b0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf2107122\" id=\"uf2107122\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Pitch 阶段</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub2a926be\" id=\"ub2a926be\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从左往右（A -&gt; B -&gt; C），用于拦截或处理元数据。</span></li><li fid=\"u51a654b1\" data-lake-id=\"uc64a44c8\" id=\"uc64a44c8\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ueb7409d9\" id=\"ueb7409d9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">Normal 阶段</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6841c8f3\" id=\"u6841c8f3\" class=\"lake-fontsize-12\" style=\"color: rgb(10, 10, 10)\">：从右往左（C -&gt; B -&gt; A），用于转换代码内容。</span></li></ul>","word_count":403,"slug":"gk462xkp328r9ndp","type":"Doc","title":"webpack 中的 Loader ，链式调用顺序会影响编译结果吗？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"Loader 的链式调用顺序不仅会影响结果，而且极其关键。在 Webpack 中，Loader 的执行遵循 “从右到左” 或 “从下到上” 的逆序执行逻辑（类似函数组合 compose(f, g, h)）。","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"codeblock\":1}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-28T07:10:08.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-28T07:16:25.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-28T07:11:19.933Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-28T07:16:25.000Z","id":258569058},"doc_digest":"qhEete9mjuV3Y9mSFaOSuyOA4-A"}